    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for Model Risk Level 2. The six non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 4 for a Class II device at MRL 2 with medium model influence. The CFD model is judged sufficiently credible to support the regulatory decision regarding worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the CPB device. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1 criterion is satisfied across all five evaluated operating points.",
